original_title: Viento Y Sol: Super Exitos en DVD
overview: Blending music videos and select live performances, this installment of the "Super Exitos" series celebrates the music of Viento Y Sol. A lively lineup of tracks includes "Par de Anillos," "Los Cielos Lloraron (Live Version)," "Callada," "Cenizas y Fuego," "Ultimas Noticias (Live Version)," "Penas," "Tu Pasado (Live Version)," "Mi Nena Va a Ser Una Mujer (Live Version)," "Camino al Cielo" and "No Se Lo Deseo a Nadie."
title: Viento Y Sol: Super Exitos en DVD
